scope_and_contents: Events pictured include: CaribFest, Re-enactment of the May 3 [1968] Bursar's Takeover, Parents Weekend, Big Brother/Big Sister, Juneteenth, African-American Cultural Tour, Senior-Parent Reception, Student Organization Recognition Banquet, Black Women's Retreat, Easter Dinner, Cecelia Hayes, Summer Academic Workshop (SAW).
series: Records of Northwestern University Black Alumni Association (NUBAA)--Photographs, 1968-2002 and undated
